resources.string: A group of individuals have decided to put their heads and resources together and have managed to create IQ Collections. This app name relates to the functions of the application as well as being similarly easy to read and remember creating a memorable application. The application will be developed to store any types of collections as well as multiple diverse collections. The chief aim of the IQ Collections application will be to have an easy to navigate and manage collection application. The IQ Collections application will be easy to catalog all the items in customizable collection templates.
